	   <tr><td colspan=2>This week there was AO patch ver. 13.6, which among other things, allowed mobs to chain cast nanos and bumped up the HP of certain NPCs. It was later discovered that a then obscure union called “the MMORPG MOB Union” or M.M.U. pushed Funcom to make the changes. I sat down with the Lab Director from AO and General V’ghera from EQ to discuss the union and that state of Mobs in general.<br><br>Roshi: Hello, thanks for your time to talk with me, I know you must spawning soon.<br><br>GV: No problem, the Uber-Guild camping my placeholder has not fully assembled yet so I have some time <br><br>LD: It is my pleasure; I managed to kill off the rabid enforcers camping me for their crat alts who want the crat suit so I have some time before more people arrive.<br><br>Roshi: My first question is, why have a MOB Union?<br><br>LD: General you have been around longer than me, why don’t you take this question.<br><br>GV: I will. Mobs are entities too. We have families and friends just like everyone else and should be treat fairly. Our job is to die so that the players can get phat lewt and become uber. Now our problem started when D00Ds started camping us non-stop for days on end and became so powerful so fast, we had to band together. Our mission is to make the game fair for us, no matter the cost of the players.<br><br>Roshi: Now, you have to care somewhat about the players.<br><br>GV: PCs are nothing about loot hungry power-leveling freaks who only care about getting the next item; if they don’t care for us, why should we care for them.<br><br>LD: Take my situation for example; I am camped non-stopped by people 50 to 100 levels higher than my level range. If I was as easy as people wanted me to be, everyone would have crat suits, but they don’t.<br><br>Roshi: Don’t you two think that casting while running, getting beat up and still hitting is a little unfair. Do you really think think that having 500k HP is also not fair.<br><br>GV: Not at all.<br><br>LD: All MOBs will be killed eventually, so we must make it as hard for them before they do. For example, what if you became a MOB that was camped endlessly, would you like a little breathing room before you were killed?<br><br>Roshi: I guess so.<br><br>GV: Our point exactly.<br><br>Roshi: Now, that we know what you are, who are members of the union?<br><br>GV: M.M.U members include Mobs in EQ, UO, DAOC, AC and AO; soon to be added SB and SW:G.&nbsp;&nbsp;Guard units and Certain NPCs are also members in the union because players can also kill them. NPCs who cannot be killed by players are excluded. The Sleeper, while being a MOB, cannot be killed so he is not a member of the union.<br>  <br>Roshi: what about single player games?<br><br>GV: Single player game MOBS do not have thier own union since different genre have different types of mobs,are not camped, and the difficulty level for those games can be changed. For example,  a MMORPG's difficulty level stays relativly the same across the whole game, so lvl 5 people will always fight lvl 5 mobs regarless. Single player games, can have hard mobs at the beginning of the game, for example.<br><br>Roshi: How exactly do you pressure the game developers to make changes?<br><br>LD: Methods includes: Blackmail, hostage taking, sexual favors,lobbying congress and sleeping in the Lincoln Bedroom in the White House.<br><br>Roshi: I though you have to give money to sleep in the White House. I don’t think the president accepts PP or Credits.<br><br>GV:  We knock out the foreign donors, then we masquerade as them, then refuse to leave the room until the president forces the developers to make the changes. This does not work so well for Funcom, since they are a foreign company. <br><br>Roshi: I see.<br><br>GV: #*)$^_$^_$^, they killed my place holder in 5 seconds flat, gotta run and kick their asses. See ya.<br><br>Roshi: Bye, how about you Director?<br><br>LD: nah noone has shown up yet.<br><br>Roshi: I think this will be the time to tell you, I have a lvl 25 crat .<br><br>LD: Your kidding right?………… What are you looking at?……. Who are  all these  new people that have shown up? What’s going on? … OH @#%^!!!!<br><br>WHACK!! CHASH!!!!! <br><br>LD: E TU ROSHI!! (dies)<br><br>Roshi: thanks guys!!<br><br>Roshi’s guild: No problem, glad we could help.<br>----<br>Roshi out.<br><br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Fri Feb  8 12:50:44 2002</em><br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
