	   <tr><td colspan=2>heres an update to the new years post below.<br><br>Jumpgate: 3D0 has cut coverage to it and netdevil(the developer) is taking over. I wonder why.....<br><br>WWOIIOnline:<br>Got voted best strategy game of the year by the readers at game spy. Aparrently, this was somewhat fixed as CRS asked readers to and player sent out a rally message on the offical message boards. I would disregard any significance of that award. No word yet on wheter WWIIOline is dead, but i will keep you posted on this.<br><br>3 MMORPGS(one might be beta) currently out that no ones heard of:<br><br>The Realm: Apparently this is a Eq like game that looks cartoonish in appearence. Since I've never really heard of this game until recently and I can't tell you where to buy it, its either 1) not very good and/or 2) bad, but its out.<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>Project Entropia: I cannot tell if this is beta or not but it looks like it is. Anyway this an &quot;AO&quot; type game. I cannot tell you much more than that though. Hey it might work it might not, I dunno.<br><br>Seducity: This is the &quot;adult&quot; MMORPG that is out there. You can most likely guess what you do in that game. Since most porn users are men, I highly doubt that most of the women avatars in the game are acual woman. Cybering with a man playing a woman seems kinda sick to me. <br><br>Well that is all for now. Next rant: The good things about EQ that I miss but would not go back for.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
